subject: Attn. Funds Beneficiary,
body:
Attn. Funds Beneficiary,
The FedEx Express Service wish to notify you that we have  received your package of ATM Visa Card worth of  Twenty Five Million United States Dollars (US$25,000,000.00) from the United Bank for Africa (UBA) as your unpaid outstanding funds since years back and we are mandated  to deliver your funds to your doorstep free of upfront or advance charges.
We wish to inform you that your ATM Card is currently available for delivery therefore 
you are required to reconfirm your details to deliver your funds as follows;
Full Name:
Current Address:
Telephone Number:
FedEx Express waits for your quick response to embark on the delivery of your funds to your doorstep without further delay..
Regards,
Oscar Keke
FedEx Express

subject: Re: Attn. Funds Beneficiary,
body:
Hello Oscar Keke,

Wow, that's quite a surprise! I can't believe I have an ATM Visa Card worth of Twenty Five Million United States Dollars waiting for me. It's like a dream come true!

I'm curious though, how did you guys manage to get hold of my package? And why was it unpaid for years back? Also, could you please explain more about this delivery process? How does it work exactly?

Looking forward to your response.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Mark
